<p>My products price is based on USD , but i want change USD to IRR with a Conversion Rate (1 USD = 3500 IRR) in shop and checkout . I found this code but it works only for product veiw and when i click on cart or checkout price change to USD .</p>  <pre><code>add_filter( 'woocommerce_get_price_html', 'wpa83367_price_html', 100, 2 ); function wpa83367_price_html( $price, $product ){     $price = get_post_meta( get_the_ID(), '_regular_price', true);     $toman = 3500;     $total = $price * $toman . ' ' . 'تومان';     return $total; } </code></pre>